(227, 'Adenovirus/RSV/HMPV/SARS-CoV-2/Influenza A+B Combo Rapid Test (Nasopharyngeal Swab)', 'The Adenovirus/RSV/HMPV/SARS-CoV-2/Influenza A+B Combo Rapid Test is a rapid chromatographic immunoassay for the qualitative detection of Adenovirus antigens, Respiratory Syncytial Virus (RSV) antigens, human metapneumovirus (HMPV) antigens,SARS-CoV-2 nucleocapsid protein, Influenza A and B antigens in human nasopharyngeal swab specimens. It is intended to aid in the rapid differential diagnosis of Adenovirus, Respiratory Syncytial Virus viral, HMPV, SARS-CoV-2, Influenza A and B infections.\r\n\r\nProduct Features\r\n\r\nFast results  \r\n\r\nEasy visual interpretation\r\n\r\nSimple operation, no equipment required \r\n\r\nHigh accuracy', 0.00, 0.00, 'https://maxmedme.com/storage/products/ON8faEgC5LOUtsVIhIvUSgPos5a8D4cRTFpAa5aY.png', 82, 2, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, '2025-04-19 20:16:47', '2025-06-14 13:49:18'),
