(229, 'Typhoid IgM Rapid Test Cassette (Whole Blood/Serum/Plasma)', 'The Typhoid IgM Rapid Test Cassette (Whole Blood/Serum/Plasma) is a rapid chromatographic immunoassay for the simultaneous detection and differentiation of IgM types of antibodiy against Salmonella typhi (S. typhi) in human whole blood, serum or plasma. It is intended to be used as a screening test as an aid in the diagnosis of infection with S. typhi. Any reactive specimen with the Typhoid IgM Rapid Test Cassette needs to be confirmed with alternative testing method.\r\n\r\nProduct Features\r\n\r\nFast results  \r\n\r\nEasy visual interpretation\r\n\r\nSimple operation, no equipment required \r\n\r\nHigh accuracy', 0.00, 0.00, 'https://maxmedme.com/storage/products/2O6Qr3L8PgGswBI7N2A7B7NcTaThxcYJwi2xIcAv.png', 82, 2, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, '2025-04-19 20:20:24', '2025-04-19 20:20:24'),
